<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=453&amp;p=2497#p2497"><![CDATA[
i dont remember the exact words, you can go over there and look it up on their legal page<br /><br />the point is, it is set up to work like this:<br /><br /><ol style="list-style-type: decimal"><li>It shows you are blacklisted from registering at all sites using stopforumspam.com, which they are using at the site you tried to register at, with a link to stopforumspam.com website</li><li>you go to the site, and it shows you a list of the most recent blacklisted email addresses, with an apparent degree of great pride, so mods can go there and gloat over seeing the people they've blacklisted.. if it was for actual spam, there would be no reason to hang out and show off the email addresses you are blacklisting, as they're all disposable &amp; meaningless anyway.. hence, right off the bat you are confronted by a site that is boasting of the emails they blacklist, yours included</li><li>You look around the site and you dont see any other reason for it being there but to tout email addresses, and you search harder and discover a way, through menu items, to eventually ask for a repeal</li><li>By this time you are foaming at the mouth at the wiseguy who would make such a retarded waste of space which seems to be very giddy about having blacklisted your email address which you've used proudly for 20 years, and is well known around the web</li><li>You find it to be nothing but slanderous, hazing, oppressive, underhanded, devious, and shrouded in hidden intent since nothing makes any sense on that site at all..</li><li>You know, then, by matter of deductive reasoning, that there must only be one use for this site, for people to destroy your online presence, out of spite, hateful grudges, vendettas, malevolence, and that you apparently have one or a group of creepy stalkers on the web who are actually moderators at some site you likely registered for for a day, posted an opposing view, and were immediately flamed, trolled, &amp; banned by the imbedded group of usual suspects / forum-mates.. </li><li>You look the site over high and low for a contact method, because at this point you dont want to appeal anything, you want to speak with the owner of the site and find out who exactly added your email to the list.. but there is no such email address to be found on the entire site.. for a site that touts banning email addresses, theirs is completely secret</li><li>You look to see what it takes to ban an email address, and so you click on &quot;submit an email address&quot;, and find it requires loads of personal information about the person being banned, that is likely never even to be found from actual spammers, and absolutely nothing from the submitter but any random APIkey</li><li>So you look for some sort of identity, any identity, of who may be behind the site.. and you find absolutely nothing.. 100% secret, hidden &amp; totaly anonymous.. as if it wasnt actually created by anyone</li><li>So you go back to that quasi-appeal option, which you already know is not really going to reach anyone worth talking to... and will probably end up in the basement of some unsuspecting mothers home who has worries about what her kid is doing down there all day, but doesnt have the heart to find out for sure... </li><li>So you tell that hidden-in-the-basement creepy little cretin exactly whats on your mind, still in disbelief as you're typing that such a site is even fathomable, and you tell him frankly, the site is slanderous &amp; nothing more than Defamatory, which is obviously illegal and nothing else, and you tell him to stop his little dorky illegal behavior and take your personal email address off of his retarded blacklist. the same as anyone would.. </li><li>Then you never receive any reply, ever.. then you go back looking for a way to hunt him down, and you by chance stumble across some obscure legal disclaimer at the back of the site that says if the request you sent him stated anything about any sort of legal problem, or legal issue, or stated any other sort of legal action, then your email address will never be removed and you will never be replied to</li><li>you are then left with no recourse...</li></ol><div align="right">-</div>its is SOOOOOO the typical moderator.. <br /><br /><br />its nothing but a big old troll.. a typical forum trap set up by mods and their cronies ... you find such little traps all over the internet, that are for no other reason than to ban users from their site, and to try and let them continue imagining they have something useful to offer the world, and are somehow in control of the entire internet.. which obviously has a few holes in it, and so they created this site where they can carry over their delinquencies into other domains and haze &amp; degrade &amp; defame you to their teeny tiny whits last end <br /><br />you know, Law is there for a reason. there is no &quot;threat of a law&quot;. the law is the law.. and there needs to be a justice if theres a law or else the law is meaningless<br /><br />and laws are made to protect people.<br /><br />and its precisely because there are numerous cretins who thrive on the misery &amp; oppression &amp; abuse &amp; manipulation of others that there needs to be laws, because their actions are such that they need to be punished, and if not by a law, then by the hand of the oppressed.<br /><br />its for their own safety &amp; protection as well.. a Lawyer is what is called when the Plaintiff or the one who has been wronged believes the wrong-doer should be shot in the head, but the one who has been wronged is a law-biding citizen or doesnt particularly think the issue is really worth the bloodshed, or the offender really worth the bullet<br /><br />thats why we have lawyers.. and why need them.. a &quot;Threat of Legal Action&quot; is something criminals say when they are about to uprooted &amp; weeded out...<br /><br />that isnt a threat...<br /><br />Sending you a photo of you in the mall creeping people out with creepy little stares from across the way, together with a bullet and a little note saying &quot;remove my email and pay me $50,000, or just pay me $50,000 by noon tomorrow, or your mom will wonder why the basement no longer smells funny&quot; is a threat.. obviously<br /><br />But its one or the other..<br /><br />I chose the legal, correct, and proper way to deal with people such as this, causing problems such as this<br /><br />in an ideal world.. there wouldnt be this kind of people who do this kind of thing.. but, reality check.. thats the way the world is.. chock full of little cretinous creeps<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=359">Tenzen</a> — Fri Apr 05, 2013 11:51 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
